so its been awhile , deciding to do another random update. i think i've meet the man of my dreams...really. but i dont know if its too soon to tell. but he is everything i've ever wanted in someone. just like in my dreams. its really crazy. i cant seem to get enough of this man. he makes me feel so good. 
my whole life i've always been the one to say they dont belive in love. im still a bit skeptical because im afriad its all going to be taken away so fast. and i think thats the one thing why im scared to even try to fall in love. like you'll never find that puzzle piece to finnish your puzzle. but i love him okay this is becoming WAY TOO GUSHY blah

yeah he's a nice fit...nuff said

Emi

my life right now is almost equal to when i was with derek. if any of you remember the little website i had made before i joined LJ. you should remember reading about how much i hated it. the only answer i can seem to give me self or best come up with is "get over it" move on and let go. losing my apt wasnt the worst thing to happen. it actually lifted up alot of stress i had built up those few months. leading me to belive i'd do better..just like everyone else..living on my own. The world is just too damn expensive to live in, with minimum wage. it almost takes a college degree to work at MCDonalds. when will what your working for surfice for what your living and fighting for? with out having to give up becuase we cant keep up with the constant headache that socity brings upon us daily? "thats life" i would once say with a smile. what bullshit i had blinded millions who have walked upon my grace. there seems to be no winning. Being nice isnt working for me anymore. i seem to get more when im mean. Fear seems to be the answer over it all. i dont know if im ready to head down that road again.
 In other spirts i have met someone who brings me sunshine almost daily. he is very sweet. even tho our time together is kinda short i guess that means i wont get sick of him too soon. i doubt i will. he is perfect for me. or so i say now..check back in a few weeks? lol. 
It feels good to write again. alot has happend some of you know some of you dont. if you dont its not that interesting. im back to picking up the pieaces to my upside down world..once again..im asuming i shall have many of these adventures....when all is over it wasnt that great..i will make it to nyc one day.

I found out we have ALOT in common! he was hot and went to take a cold shower i left a message saying "dont get too curious while your in there" and we got to chatting bout things when he came back . i discussed about why how i was shy and he said he was to. and i go what do you have to be shy about (he asked me first) and he goes " my deformaity" so at first i was thinking what does he have a pussy too? rofll but no thats not the case.

His left side of his face is paralized he asked if i had noticed i told him no (because i hadint) he said his left eye kinda twitches (never seen it do it) and that he doesnt smile on his left side ( i thought it was just a cute smirk?) and i said i never noticed and he was still cute to me =D because he is! but yeah

we agreed there wasnt any pressure to anything and that we would go with the flow with whatever happens. haha im excited i really like haggin with him.
